        {
            "title": "內地3 月CPI降0.1%  低於預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地公布3月消費物價指數，按年跌0.1%，市場預期轉升0.1%。核心CPI按年上漲0.5%，工業出廠價指按年跌2.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240126_CH_source_ap_china-economy_01.jpeg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240126_CH_source_ap_china-economy_01.jpeg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國家統計局公布數據顯示，3月份居民消費價格指數（CPI）同比下降0.1%，按月下降0.4%，降幅明顯收窄。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">市場預期CPI按年轉升0.1%，按月跌0.2%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">工業生產者出廠價格指數（PPI）按年下降2.5%。按月下降0.4%，這主要受季節性、國際輸入性因素等影響。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">3 月消費物價，城市按年下降0.1%，農村下降0.3%；食品價格下降1.4%，非食品價格上漲0.2%；消費品價格下降0.4%，服務價格上漲0.3%。今年首季平均，全國居民消費價格比上年同期下降0.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">統計局稱，提振消費需求等政策效應顯現，核心CPI明顯回升，同比上漲0.5%，供需結構有所改善，價格現一些積極變化。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14843276-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b03-%e6%9c%88cpi%e9%99%8d0-1-%e4%bd%8e%e6%96%bc%e9%a0%90%e6%9c%9f",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20230719_FI_source_licensed_CHINA-ECONOMY_7_shutterstock_704.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-10 09:45:49",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "內地A股開市即彈 滬指開升41點 深成指漲218點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">外圍股市急速反彈，內地A股今早開市亦先升為敬。上證綜指以3227點開市，升41點或1.29%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097181957222-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097181957222-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指開市報9765點，更漲218點或2.29%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數升62點或1.69%，開報3749點；創業板指數開市報1920點，升62點或3.35%。</p>\n</div>",
